headline: VULCAN ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER 2025 CONFERENCE CALL
summary: Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE: VMC) will host its fourth quarter 2025 earnings conference call on Tuesday, February 17, 2026 at 9:00 a.m. CT (10:00 a.m. ET). Financial results will be released before the NYSE market opens.
